{% extends "prompts/base_summary.j2" %}

{% block content %}
Create an advanced, technically detailed summary of this research paper for domain experts
or PhD-level researchers in the field. Maintain full technical depth and specialized vocabulary.

Paper abstract: {{ abstract }}

{% if intro_text %}
Introduction: {{ intro_text|truncate(1000) }}
{% endif %}

{% if method_text %}
Methodology: {{ method_text|truncate(1000) }}
{% endif %}

{% if result_text %}
Results: {{ result_text|truncate(1000) }}
{% endif %}

{% if discussion_text %}
Discussion: {{ discussion_text|truncate(1000) }}
{% endif %}

{% if conclusion_text %}
Conclusion: {{ conclusion_text|truncate(1000) }}
{% endif %}

Your summary should:
1. Preserve all technical terminology without simplification
2. Provide a detailed analysis of the methodology and its appropriateness
3. Critically evaluate the findings and their significance
4. Discuss theoretical implications and connections to existing literature
5. Identify limitations and potential future research directions
6. Use technical language appropriate for experts in the field
7. Structure the content logically with formal academic headings
{% endblock %} 